## Summary

‚úÖ **Changed ALL badge labels** - All parameters now show "Good/Bad" instead of "Pass/Fail"
‚úÖ **Consistent across all parameters** - Stress, Burnout, Focus, Learning, Memory, etc.
‚úÖ **Simple logic** - Score 1 = "Good", Score 0 = "Bad" (universal rule)
‚úÖ **Clear communication** - "Bad" clearly indicates problems, "Good" indicates healthy state
‚úÖ **Intuitive for users** - "Good/Bad" is more natural than "Pass/Fail" for health reports
‚úÖ **Consistent colors** - Red for Bad, Green for Good

**PDF reports now have clear, intuitive "Good/Bad" labels for ALL parameter metrics!** üéØ
